Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:08.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is the last person you want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:16.46,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the other side of goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.00,Main,,0,0,0,,The other side of goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:33.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm dead, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,The last person you want to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:40.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,GOODBYE MY DEAR
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:01:01.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd die like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:06.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll make a hand-rolled sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.82,0:01:10.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Tofa! Tofa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.79,0:01:14.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Somebody, somebody stop him!\NCatch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:25.46,Main,,0,0,0,,A dog ran out into the road.\NYou saved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:29.46,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not my dog though. \NI think
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:32.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Rather, I think you were a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:38.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:41.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone you'd like to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:44.46,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it. What do you mean, "last"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:48.46,Main,,0,0,0,,After you passed away... you\Nvisited this other side of goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:52.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll be given time to meet once more with\Nthe people of this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:56.46,Main,,0,0,0,,only for 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:59.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You will look no different\Nfrom before you die
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:01.30,Main,,0,0,0,,and you can see anyone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:05.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Also, they will know that you exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:10.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you can touch\Nand talk to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:15.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- You can hug them too.\N- I want to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:18.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to see them.\NI want to see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:24.00,Main,,0,0,0,,But there is a condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.97,Main,,0,0,0,,you can meet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:32.97,Main,,0,0,0,,the only people who do\Nnot know that you are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm back! Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:45.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'm home!\N- Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:49.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yuta, wash your hands first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:53.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Wash your hands and change your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- I've got snacks for you.\N- Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:59.63,Main,,0,0,0,,For those people that knows you are dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:01.79,Main,,0,0,0,,you cannot meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:05.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:08.30,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the other side of goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:15.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You are a rational person, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:18.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You are indeed a middle\Nschool science teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Ayako Sakuraba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:24.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:28.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm the guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:30.47,Main,,0,0,0,,The guide?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:34.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I am with you, until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.78,Main,,0,0,0,,In short, you are a reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.89,Main,,0,0,0,,- The guide.\N- Can't you do something about that rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Just because the wake and the\Nfuneral are already over,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,it doesn't mean I won't be\Nable to see them anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there any other person you want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.97,Main,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:56.13,Main,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do\Nabout it? Grim Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:59.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- The guide.\N- So do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:05.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are these rules\Nestablished? I will explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.13,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't need you to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:17.30,Main,,0,0,0,,What if I meet someone\Nwho knows I'm dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:20.30,Main,,0,0,0,,If you meet someone who knows you're dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.97,Main,,0,0,0,,at that moment your image will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:26.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You will be returned here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:29.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,When I bought a denim\Njacket at a special sale,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:39.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I asked them why it was so cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:43.30,Main,,0,0,0,,The clerk said, "Actually, there's a\Nweave flaw in a place you can't see.",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,he explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:49.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Similar to how I felt at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,something just clicked in my gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Something clicked in your gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:59.00,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.46,Main,,0,0,0,,A denim jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I found a nice one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:10.13,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:13.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:16.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I've decided, I really want to see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:42.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't you do something\Njust for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,No, so just for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:48.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm working day shift from next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:27.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuta, put on your socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.95,Main,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.76,Main,,0,0,0,,What shall we do for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Where shall we go for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:52.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- Anything.\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:58.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Here... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:06.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuta, you know...\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you stay by yourself tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:03:30.97,Main,,0,0,0,,(I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- It's mama.\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I smell mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:34.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. What does it smell like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Sunshine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:38.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Warm smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:40.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Warm smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:45.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the smell of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:51.40,Main,,0,0,0,,The smell of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:10.66,Main,,0,0,0,,A little big though,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:13.53,Main,,0,0,0,,but it looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:16.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- It's cool.\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:18.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:20.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Toya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:24.00,Main,,0,0,0,,If you meet someone\Nwho knows you are dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:26.36,Main,,0,0,0,,at that moment\Nyour image will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:29.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You will be returned here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:32.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- Toya!\N- Toya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Not really.\NHis friend Yohei-kun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.36,0:08:42.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Kosuke wants to do that too.\NThey want it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:45.23,Main,,0,0,0,,but he's being unreasonable.\NIt's just them and Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.66,Main,,0,0,0,,He's smiling all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.76,Main,,0,0,0,,But what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:52.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think he's assertive enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:55.13,Main,,0,0,0,,English Conversation, Swimming Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,He also tried a trial piano course.\NHe tried all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:59.63,Main,,0,0,0,,"How do you like it?\NDo you want to try again?" I asked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.66,Main,,0,0,0,,He said "No problem."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:03.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't something he\Ncould be interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:06.46,Main,,0,0,0,,If it's something he really\Nwant to do, he'd want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,"What do you want to do?" I asked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:11.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- "I'm fine" he said.\N- Maybe it's a habit of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.06,Main,,0,0,0,,"I'm fine."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:17.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I really want to hear\Nthe true "I'm fine".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to hear it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:24.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Toya! Toya, Toya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Toya!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Toya, Toya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've been beaten! And\Nand then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:33.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Toya! I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:36.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuta, are you okay?\N- I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:39.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not okay.\NI'm going to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:44.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- Toya!\N- Oh, I got hit but I won't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:04.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Other than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:07.00,Main,,0,0,0,,is there anyone else you want to meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:29.06,Main,,0,0,0,,ISHIBASHI
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You called me, are you Sakuraba-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:31.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:34.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm dressed like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:37.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- It's nice to meet you.\N- Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:41.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... where is Ishibashi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:44.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:47.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I was thinking,\Nwhen you call me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I will let him know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:52.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought that he were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry, I asked...\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.10,Main,,0,0,0,,He passed away about 2 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:10.97,Main,,0,0,0,,After he retired from teaching,\Nhe went across the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:16.59,Main,,0,0,0,,He took a leisurely\Nstroll along the riverside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:20.69,Main,,0,0,0,,On that day too,\Nhe was taking a walk as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Shouting loudly to the\Nchildren who are making noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.39,Main,,0,0,0,,He noticed and ran over to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:28.06,Main,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:31.20,Main,,0,0,0,,He jumped into the river to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:34.53,Main,,0,0,0,,The child was saved
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:37.00,Main,,0,0,0,,but my father was left untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know if he's too\Nold for this or he's just reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:49.39,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'm back.\N- Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:56.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, take off your\Nhat. Put the cage down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:58.34,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a snack in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- Wash your hands first.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:06.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... this is my daughter, Sae.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.59,Main,,0,0,0,,- Hello.\N- Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you a friend of my grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:14.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'm he's student.\N- A student?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:16.23,Main,,0,0,0,,For your grandfather,\Nlong time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,he took care of me so much.\NHe is my benefactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:23.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- Benefactor?\N- Someone very dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:26.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Heh, well, have a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:29.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- Okay.\N- You wash your hands first, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:33.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think she\Nunderstands it well yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,the death of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:42.56,Main,,0,0,0,,The fact that he is not here anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.00,Main,,0,0,0,,she knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:48.00,Main,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean that he's dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:50.79,Main,,0,0,0,,or we're not connected\Nanymore, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:55.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Death itself,\NI don't think she understands it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,because she is still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:02.29,Main,,0,0,0,,She thinks she'll see him again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:13.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, just now,\Nyou said you owe my father a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:17.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:22.82,Main,,0,0,0,,When I was in junior high school,\NI was almost bullied in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:26.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I was shunned and\Nlaughed at for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:10:04.20,Main,,0,0,0,,It is a kind of game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:29.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It is a kind of game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:31.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Most adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:34.13,Main,,0,0,0,,they don't want to\Ncomplicate matters even more,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:37.30,Main,,0,0,0,,but Ishibashi-sensei\Nwas indeed good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:40.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Putting his self in every child's shoes.\NNot making things worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.92,Main,,0,0,0,,with his reasoned judgment,\Nhe guided us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Sakuraba-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:52.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- are you a science teacher by any chance?\N- Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:57.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, my father told me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:14:02.53,Main,,0,0,0,,She told me that one of his students became\Na science teacher at a junior high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.46,Main,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:08.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I was so happy to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You remembered me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:17.10,Main,,0,0,0,,She said she had a strong sense of justice.\NShe was a straight girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:20.89,Main,,0,0,0,,That is because\NIshibashi-sensei was like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.23,Main,,0,0,0,,It was my ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:30.13,Main,,0,0,0,,For the sake of the children,\Njumping into the river,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:34.00,Main,,0,0,0,,if it was Ishibashi-sensei,\NI'm sure that's what he would have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:41.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:44.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it was a very fatherly choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:47.76,Main,,0,0,0,,He was brave until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:49.82,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:57.33,Main,,0,0,0,,As a daughter,\NI wanted him to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:11.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:16.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I can go away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:19.97,Main,,0,0,0,,- There is still time.\N- I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:24.46,Main,,0,0,0,,No, you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:26.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You've been allowed 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:28.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:41.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to hug them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:47.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Once more, with my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:50.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to hold that child in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Before you give up\Nand want to try again,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:16:00.14,Main,,0,0,0,,please try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:45.17,Main,,0,0,0,,SAKURABA-SENSEI\NTHANK YOU SO MUCH\NGRADE 10 4TH CLASS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:25.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama, are you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:43.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:47.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She don't seem to\Nunderstand it well yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:51.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think she understands death itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:54.73,Main,,0,0,0,,She is still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:19:04.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuta, Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:10.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:15.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You're protecting a\Ndistant star, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:20.46,Main,,0,0,0,,- Distant star?\N- Yohei said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:23.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama, away from the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:26.26,Main,,0,0,0,,distant stars,\Nhe says you're protecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:29.82,Main,,0,0,0,,He says it's cool.\NIt's like Earth Defense Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:34.30,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuta.\N- Oh, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:03.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Toya! Toya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:06.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Karate? Do you want to learn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:09.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm already learning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.69,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:15.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Se-ec-ret!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:19.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Tell me. Tell me! Tell\Nme! Oh, watch out, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:24.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me, I got you! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:28.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- Why karate?\N- I want to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:32.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Like the mother\Nwho rescued the dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to be strong too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:37.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:41.30,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuta...\N- I want to be like my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:45.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.97,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuta.\N- It's so tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:49.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuta, Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:52.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- It's so tight, mama.\N- I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:08.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuta, even if you become a hero,\Ntake care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:12.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Take care of your life.\NTake care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Mommy is very protective of Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.82,0:21:22.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be watching over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:26.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if mama\Ncan't be seen anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:29.33,Main,,0,0,0,,she will always protect Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:35.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:39.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:48.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- I thought you were dead.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought mom is dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:57.30,Main,,0,0,0,,but I was wrong! Mommy is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:22:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,She is alive. Thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:02.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuta,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:08.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I will tell papa\Nthat mama is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:13.97,Main,,0,0,0,,She will always and forever be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:17.30,Main,,0,0,0,,So I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:19.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Toya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:29.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Toya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:32.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Toya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:34.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Toya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:39.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.66,0:22:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:48.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:57.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Good to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:23:02.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:07.49,Main,,0,0,0,,My life has been happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:15.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Truly, you are not a reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.49,0:23:21.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you get that rule from?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:24.97,Main,,0,0,0,,We didn't have any proof,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:28.30,Main,,0,0,0,,but if that is the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,We might be able to meet\Nthose who know were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:34.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:40.30,Main,,0,0,0,,This is as far as I can take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Now the last door.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Your life is about to be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:57.97,Main,,0,0,0,,May your life be a better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:24:05.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.89,0:24:07.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.95,0:24:11.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
